data.description: Don’t Miss This Entertainers Dream!! Custom 5 BR home situated on a level, .92 acre lot with private outdoor oasis including a heated pool (completely updated) & new hot tub. Step into the beautiful 2-story foyer with open floor plan. Completely updated main floor boasts great room featuring a gorgeous gas fireplace with built-in cabinetry, private office, formal dining room, gorgeous Kitchen w/ large island, Breakfast area & keeping room overlooking your private outdoor oasis. Walk-in butler pantry & laundry off 3-car garage. Main level master with gas fireplace & private 2-car garage with separate pool access, his & her walk-in closets w/ island, 2nd laundry room & 2 full master baths. Upper level access by staircase or elevator featuring additional 4 BRs, loft, large bonus room, and billiard room. Storage galore!
